ned>). Ср. <mentioned xml:lang="krc-x-balkar"><lang/> <w>ʒatma</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="krc-x-balkar"><w>zatma</w> <gloss><q>навес</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="krc-x-balkar"><w/> <gloss><q>балкон</q></gloss></mentioned>.</etym><etym xml:lang="en">From <mentioned xml:lang="trk"><lang/> <w>čatma</w> <gloss><q>tent</q></gloss></mentioned> (from <mentioned xml:lang="trk"><lang/> <w>čatmaq</w> <gloss><q>build</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="trk"><w/> <gloss><q>erect</q></gloss></mentioned>). Cf. <mentioned xml:lang="krc-x-balkar"><lang/> <w>ʒatma</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="krc-x-balkar"><w>zatma</w> <gloss><q>hovel</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="krc-x-balkar"><w/> <gloss><q>balcony</q></gloss></mentioned>.</etym></entry></body></text></TEI>